1.e-2				260.25			.3531
5.e-2				268.11			.3512
1.e-1				274.46			.3510
1.15e-1				276.21			.3513
3.e-1				287.91			.3575			


NOW add methane incrementally as before (from 3.e-1 bar, ~288K)
